===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# The act or process of [[punish]]ing, imposing and/or applying a [[sanction]].
#: {{ux|en|The naughty children were given a '''punishment''' by their teachers.}}
# A [[penalty]] to punish wrongdoing, especially for [[crime]].
#: {{ux|en|a light '''punishment'''}}
#: {{ux|en|a harsh ''punishement'''}}
# A [[suffering]] by [[pain]] or [[loss]] imposed as [[retribution]]
# {{lb|en|figuratively}} Any [[treatment]] or experience so [[harsh]] it feels like being punished; rough handling
#: {{ux|en|a vehicle that can take a lot of '''punishment'''}}

